messages.message:
@Weiming Wu @hannah I noticed a change went into UAT from this PR (https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/62377) where we made the "Create" project button on the home page a dropdown. Two comments here:
1. Are we sure we want this to be a dropdown with all the options (create blank project, create from template, etc)? This is the first place a new user could create a project from, do we want it to just create a blank project by default?
2. If we do want this to be a dropdown, can we cherry pick a change to add a chevron and make sure the menu is aligned correctly?
